                ></a>
                <a
                    target="_BLANK"
                    href="https://www.twitch.tv/ZonianMidian"
                    class="fa-brands fa-twitch"
                ></a>
                <a
                    target="_BLANK"
                    href="https://www.github.com/ZonianMidian"
                    class="fa-brands fa-github"
                ></a>
                <a
                    target="_BLANK"
                    href="https://discord.com/users/651500580161716224"
                    class="fa-brands fa-discord"
                ></a>
            </div>
            <p>Any questions or suggestions are welcome ;)</p>
        </blockquote>
    </div>
</body>
